                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                            <locus from="139r" to="143r"/>
                            <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3852KingList">King list (general record)</title>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez"><hi rend="rubric">በስመ፡ ስሉስ፡ ፡ ፩አምላክ። </hi>ወእምዝ፡ ንጽሕፍ፡ ዓመታተ፡ ነገሥተ፡ አክሱም። ዘአርዌ፡ 
                                <hi rend="rubric">፼</hi> ዓመት። ዘብእሲ፡ አንገቦ፡ ዘቀተሎ፡ ለአርዌ፡ <hi rend="rubric">፪፻</hi>። </incipit>
                            <explicit xml:lang="gez">ውናግ፡ ሰገደ፡ ወ፡ ዘተሰምየ፡ ልብነ፡ ድን<pb n="143r"/>
                                ግል፡ ፳ወ<supplied reason="lost">፫</supplied>፡ ዓመት። ወተጽሕፈት፡ ዛቲ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ በእደዊሁ፡ ለቀሲስ፡ 
                                <persName role="scribe" cert="low" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11227ZaraLe">ዘርአ፡ ልዑል።</persName> 
                                በ፻፹፡ ወ<supplied reason="lost">፫</supplied>፡ ዓመተ፡ ምሕረት፡ በ<supplied reason="lost">ሉቃ</supplied>ስ፡ ወንጌላዊ። 
                                ወዘሰረቃ፡ ወተአገላ፡ ውጉዘ፡ ይኩን፡ በአፋሆሙ፡ ለጴጥሮስ፡ ወጳውሎስ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም። </explicit>
                            <note>The explicit contains a twofold date and a name of a scribe. Alas the date is not complete, because in several instances numerals
                                have been intentionally erased, but can according to <bibl><seg type="journalArticle"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Marrassini1987manoscrittietiopici"/><title level="a">I manoscritti etiopici della Biblioteca Medicea Laurenziana di Firenze</title><title level="j">Rassegna di Studi Etiopici</title><author><forename>Paolo</forename><surname>Marrassini</surname></author><date>1987</date><biblScope unit="volume">31</biblScope><biblScope unit="page">69-110</biblScope><note type="url">http://www.jstor.org/stable/41299700</note><note type="tags"><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">bm:Marrassini1987manoscrittietiopici</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">Florence</note></note><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">bm:Marrassini1987manoscrittietiopici</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">Florence</note><citedRange unit="page">77</citedRange></bibl> be reconstructed to the year 23 of the reign of Lǝbna Dǝngǝl and the year 183,
                                the two dates that both give the year <date cert="medium" calendar="gregorian">1530</date> as date of production of the manuscript. 
                                Whether the agency of the scribe <persName role="scribe" cert="low" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11227ZaraLe">Zarʾa Lǝʿul</persName> 
                                on the other hand relates to the entire manuscript or yet alone to the last three folios is not clear as well. Since the last bifolium 
                                <locus target="#q20"/> is written with less care and with another pen, it may have been written by another hand and represent 
                                a later addition.</note>
                            <note>According to <bibl><seg type="journalArticle"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Marrassini1987manoscrittietiopici"/><title level="a">I manoscritti etiopici della Biblioteca Medicea Laurenziana di Firenze</title><title level="j">Rassegna di Studi Etiopici</title><author><forename>Paolo</forename><surname>Marrassini</surname></author><date>1987</date><biblScope unit="volume">31</biblScope><biblScope unit="page">69-110</biblScope><note type="url">http://www.jstor.org/stable/41299700</note><note type="tags"><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">bm:Marrassini1987manoscrittietiopici</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">Florence</note></note><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">bm:Marrassini1987manoscrittietiopici</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">Florence</note><citedRange unit="page">77</citedRange></bibl>
                                the list as far as the Kings of Aksum are concerned, corresponds to <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3855KingList">King list C</title> and <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3853KingList">King list A</title> 
                                according to Conti Rossinis categorization 
                                in <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/KKKATHSD"><seg type="journalArticle"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:ContiRossini1909Listes"/><title level="a">Les listes des rois d’Aksoum</title><title level="j">Journal Asiatique</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Carlo</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Conti Rossini</t:surname></author><date>1909</date><biblScope unit="volume">Dixième Série, 14</biblScope><biblScope unit="page">263-320</biblScope><citedRange unit="page">268 and 285</citedRange></bibl>.</note>
                        </msItem>
